description: Guernsey's director of public health is placed on the delayed Queen's Birthday Honours List.
title: Birthday Honours: Guernsey health director's MBE for Covid response
title_page: Birthday Honours: Guernsey health director's MBE for Covid response - BBC News
maintext: The list was originally due to be released in June, but was postponed by UK Prime Minister Boris Johnson to allow for nominations of people for their contributions during the pandemic.
